high_descs: Turn right, go straight, turn right at the sink drying rack.
Take the knife from the rack.
Turn right, go straight to the wall, turn right, go straight to the white table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Turn around, go straight to the fridge.
Put the knife in the middle shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go straight to the white table.
Take a slice of potato from the white table.
Turn around, go straight and to the left to the microwave next to the fridge.
Cook the potato in the microwave, take the potato from the microwave.
Go to the fridge on the right of the microwave.
Put the potato on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk over to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife next to the sink.
Go to the counter next to the door on the right.
Slice the potato on the counter behind the spatula.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the butter knife in the fridge.
Go back to the counter to the right of the door.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Take the potato slice to the micorwave.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave.
Go to the fridge.
Put the cooked potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right 90 degrees and walk through the kitchen to the wall, then turn right 90 degrees and face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the left side of the covered portion of the sink.
Holding the knife, turn right and walk towards the door.  Turn right to face the table on the right hand side of the door.
Slice the potato that is on the back left corner of the table, behind the spatula.
Turn around to stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door (bottom door), place the knife on the second shelf from the top, then close the door.
Turn around 180 degrees to stand in front of the table.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Turn right, go forward a few steps, then turn right to face the microwave.

Open the microwave door, put the potato slice in the microwave to the right of the egg, and close the door.  Microwave the slice for a few seconds, then open the door and take out the slice.  Shut the microwave door.
Holding the potato slice, turn right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door (bottom door), and put the potato slice on the top shelf in front of the skillet.  Close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato slice and knife into the fridge.
